{"tid":2136422,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Patreon 就嚟收皮","createTime":"2020-08-02T06:44:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-02T19:25:11.000Z","uid":178690,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"6e772a66ea678febf5af10e87cf5010db19a41bf","tid":2136422,"uid":178690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T06:44:05.000Z","msg":"首先貼新聞links 上嚟先<br />\n<a href=\"https://ussanews.com/News1/2020/07/30/patreon-loses-lawsuit-with-owen-benjamin-fans-likely-to-pay-millions-in-arbitration-and-legal-fees/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fussanews.com%2FNews1%2F2020%2F07%2F30%2Fpatreon-loses-lawsuit-with-owen-benjamin-fans-likely-to-pay-millions-in-arbitration-and-legal-fees%2F&d=aFheyUS8Hi5o9a%2F4VMBAnazbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=a5d35304\" target=\"_blank\">https://ussanews.com/News1/2020/07/30/patreon-loses-lawsuit-with-owen-benjamin-fans-likely-to-pay-millions-in-arbitration-and-legal-fees/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cernovich.com/patreon-lawsuit-owen-benjamin/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cernovich.com%2Fpatreon-lawsuit-owen-benjamin%2F&d=aFheyUS8Hi5o9a%2F4VMBAnazbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=90e6663f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cernovich.com/patreon-lawsuit-owen-benjamin/</a><br />\n唔想睇字嘅巴打可以睇呢條片<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Px46aTSuX2g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DPx46aTSuX2g&d=aFheyUS8Hi5o9a%2F4VMBAnazbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=4c28aede\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Px46aTSuX2g</a><br />\nTLDR，Patreon 最近被判敗訴，會因為仲裁(Arbitration)關係而要畀成百萬以上美金<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n事源係Patreon ban  咗Owen Benjamin，Benjamin 就叫佢啲fans 去告Patreon。<br />\n<br />\n根據Patreon 嘅TOS，任何法律訴訟都要以仲裁方式去處理。<br />\n根據加州法律，Patreon 要負責畀仲裁費用，每個仲裁case費用最多可以去到1萬美金。<br />\n<br />\n有72個fans 走去同Patreon 講佢地會申請仲裁。Patreon 調番轉頭告個72個fans，諗住可以令佢地嘅仲裁申請無效，同時申請禁制令唔畀其他人申請仲裁。<br />\n<br />\n係7月30號，加州法院判Patreon 敗訴，Patreon 因為咁要處理每一個仲裁。<br />\n<br />\n點解話Patreon 要畀成百萬以上美金？因為Patreon 係呢單野之前都有ban 人，而家畀人ban 嘅creators 個班fans 都可以申請仲裁。<br />\n<br />\n咁究竟有幾多人？畀人ban 嘅creators 入面有兩個比較高知名度，Carl Benjamin (Sargon of Akkard) 同埋Lauren Southern。Lauren Southern 我搵唔到佢之前係Patreon 有幾多sub，但係根據Carl Benjamin 係SubscribeStar 嘅sub count︰<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NjawiGW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNjawiGW.png&h=3aa17e73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而Lauren Southern 本人已經準備緊告鳩Patreon<br />\n<a href=\"https://ussanews.com/News1/2020/08/01/exclusive-lauren-southern-taking-first-steps-to-sue-patreon/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fussanews.com%2FNews1%2F2020%2F08%2F01%2Fexclusive-lauren-southern-taking-first-steps-to-sue-patreon%2F&d=aFheyUS8Hi5o9a%2F4VMBAnazbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=baa889bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://ussanews.com/News1/2020/08/01/exclusive-lauren-southern-taking-first-steps-to-sue-patreon/</a><br />\nPatreon 真係會畀人告到破產<br />\n<br />\n而家係度同大家講，快啲跳船，轉去SubscribeStar。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.subscribestar.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.subscribestar.com%2F&d=aFheyUS8Hi5o9a%2F4VMBAnazbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=a36a4a47\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.subscribestar.com/</a><br />\n而電子雞可以考慮轉用OnlyFans，以免污染SubscribeStar<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://onlyfans.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fonlyfans.com%2F&d=aFheyUS8Hi5o9a%2F4VMBAnazbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=77298f08\" target=\"_blank\">https://onlyfans.com/</a>"},{"pid":"3542e67516fe2d69db091861ad203708b7d009df","tid":2136422,"uid":61653,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T06:46:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />班雞雞同雞蟲典蒜"},{"pid":"5662f8e8e5016bae4f532d493f01547a1ddec50d","tid":2136422,"uid":178690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T06:49:45.000Z","msg":"link 入面有好多法律terms，唔係law 撚唔識點轉番做中文。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果有巴打熟嘅可以講多啲。"},{"pid":"ae4234c920ad003d551aca7871d745393df289e2","tid":2136422,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3542e67516fe2d69db091861ad203708b7d009df","tid":2136422,"uid":61653,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T06:46:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />班雞雞同雞蟲典蒜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T06:50:22.000Z","msg":"onlyfans"},{"pid":"d1014089c8797cd4d6bf9680467fffe6e0082340","tid":2136422,"uid":178690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3542e67516fe2d69db091861ad203708b7d009df","tid":2136422,"uid":61653,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T06:46:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />班雞雞同雞蟲典蒜"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T06:50:43.000Z","msg":"轉用OnlyFans<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根本就係有得睇冇得食嘅141<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4f8cc44f8f1549f2cf26cc990b8812d5fe30f24","tid":2136422,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T06:53:48.000Z","msg":"d人咩事被ban既？"},{"pid":"e0df3965f7d2bd02eafadbced0a6b1